<div class="question">
  <div class="title">
    Question
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    I would like to program an application in which you can control values
    of red, green and blue with trackbars. How can I do that?
  </div>
</div>

<h2>
  Answer 1
</h2>

<p>
  Drop three TrackBars on a form. Set <var>Min</var> to 0, <var>Max</var> to
  255. Drop a <var>TImage</var> on the form. Then try this code:
</p>

<div class="frame">
